class_description:
Signals that an error has been reached unexpectedly
 while parsing.

params.param_description: the position where the error is found while parsing.

Methods.method_description:
Constructs a ParseException with the specified detail message and
 offset.
 A detail message is a String that describes this particular exception.

return_description: the position where the error was found

Methods.method_description: Returns the position where the error was found.
